($$Paradox Museum London$$, $$Paradox Museum London$$, null, 51.49970640000001, -0.1639623, $$Museums & culture$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Paradox%20Museum%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/176858$$, null, null, 0, $$Families and children$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Exit reality. Enter fun at Paradox Museum London! Step into 50+ hands-on illusions, interactive rooms and reality-defying photo moments in Knightsbridge, directly opposite Harrods. This summer, Paradox Pier has landed! A limited-time seaside-inspired experience where hidden clues, playful surprises and the new Paradox Postcard Trail appear across the museum. Go tiny or giant in the Ames Room, get lost in the Mirror Maze, walk through the Tube Room, defy gravity and capture photos your friends won’t believe are real. Perfect for families, friends, tourists and anyone looking for a fun indoor London day out this summer. Add-Ons 🏖 Paradox Postcard Trail : find the beach in Knightsbridge! Pick up your Impossible Postcard, hunt for hidden seaside clues across selected exhibits, match them to your postcard and claim your Paradox Pier prize at the gift shop. Available for a limited time this summer. 🌀 Zero Gravity Room : Defy balance, movement, and gravity! Complete your mission, capture a video, and take home a verified souvenir pass. 🚀 🔄 Flex Ticket : Make your ticket flexible and reschedule your visit anytime on the same day. Limited capacity, pre-booking recommended. One add-on per person. 🛍️ Merch Bundle : Save 25% on souvenirs online! Includes a Bendy Pencil, Paradox Hourglass, Mind Game Puzzle and Paradox Spinner! Highlights 🌏 Visited by 3 million people worldwide 🤯 Explore 50+ immersive paradoxes and challenge reality 👪 Play in impossible rooms: stand upside down, disappear, and snap epic selfies! 🤳 Experience the Zero Gravity Room: feel like you're walking in space! (add-on required) 🧠 Challenge yourself and think outside the box 🎁 Save 25% on Paradox Museum souvenirs when buying the Merch Bundle Add-on online! General Info ⏳ Duration: approx. 90 minutes 📍 Location: Paradox Museum London 👤 Age: all ages welcome! Children must be with a paying adult. Photo ID required for minors 14–17. Kids under 4 enter free. All attendees, including toddlers and infants, must have a valid ticket, and entry may be refused if you arrive without tickets for every member of your party and we are at capacity 🌀 Under 18s need adult consent for the Zero Gravity exhibit 👉 Plan a birthday party at Paradox Museum here ♿ Accessibility: wheelchair accessible. Please check the FAQs, some exhibits are not fully accessible. Personal assistant/support worker pass available here (proof required) ❓ Consult the FAQs here 🎁 Treat your friends and family to a Paradox Museum gift card here Description Step into Paradox Museum London and see the world from a new perspective. Explore mind-bending exhibits like the Infinity Well, Zero Gravity Room, Paradox Sofa, and Paradox Tunnel, where reality is redefined and gravity is challenged. Each exhibit pushes your perception and creativity. Get your tickets now for this immersive experience!$$, $$GBP 27.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/176858$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/762a31c4-058b-11f0-9995-2a2765d93322.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/176858$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$House of Dreamers$$, $$Immerse LDN, Excel Waterfront, London$$, null, 51.50845979699808, 0.02987898333391933, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Immerse%20LDN%2C%20Excel%20Waterfront%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/628172$$, null, null, 0, $$all ages are welcome! - Children must be accompanied by a paying adult ♿ Accessibility: the exhibition route is accessible for wheelchair users and visitors with reduced mobility$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ After inspiring over 2 million visitors worldwide, House of Dreamers arrives in London for the very first time. Step into a first-of-its-kind immersive exhibition by Elena & Giulia Sella, featuring 16 breathtaking installations designed to awaken your imagination, stir your emotions and celebrate the power of dreams. 🔓 Doors open to the public! Get your tickets now! Highlights 🌈 16 Immersive Dreamscapes: Journey through a series of whimsical, pastel-drenched installations designed to spark wonder and ignite your imagination. 🫧 Giant Pink Ball Pit: Dive into a massive, vibrant pink pool, the ultimate photo-ready experience designed to help you find joy in the present moment. 🍄 Fairytale Forest & Cloud Swings: Wander through kaleidoscopic toadstools, discover light-projected waterfalls, and literally swing among ethereal white clouds. 🤖 Cutting-Edge Interactive Tech: Use the 'Dream Machine' or watch your own animal sketches come to life and roam through magical digital landscapes. 👪 Families are welcome: free add-on ticket available for Toddlers (0-3 y.o.) 🎁 Gift memories to someone special! Purchase a gift card for House of Dreamers here General Info 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector 🕒 Time: - Monday–Thursday: 10 AM–7 PM - Friday & Public Holidays: 10 AM–8 PM - Saturday: 9 AM–8 PM - Sunday: 9 AM–7 PM ⏲ Please note that last slot begins 75 minutes before closing time ⏳ Duration: 60-90 minutes 📍 Location: Immerse LDN, Excel Waterfront 🚗 Parking is available on-site and can be booked in advance here 👤 Age requirement: all ages are welcome! - Children must be accompanied by a paying adult ♿ Accessibility: the exhibition route is accessible for wheelchair users and visitors with reduced mobility. However, due to the nature of some installations, certain areas may be less suitable for guests with specific access requirements ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description House of Dreamers is an immersive journey into your own dreams. Guests of all ages are invited on an extraordinary journey through 16 immersive installations, brought to life through exclusive DreamBand and AI-powered technology. As you explore, your DreamBand unlocks magical touchpoints along the way, revealing personalised, interactive moments designed to make your experience even more meaningful, memorable, and truly unique. Begin your journey towards making your greatest dreams come true… and remember, everything starts with a dream.$$, $$GBP 22.90 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/628172$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/60a8017c-76bf-11f1-9fc1-062627165393.png$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/628172$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Babylon Park: London’s Underground Theme Park$$, $$Babylon Park London$$, null, 51.54221709999999, -0.144926, $$Parks & outdoor play$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Babylon%20Park%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/309703$$, null, null, 0, $$Babylon Park is perfect for adults and children of all ages$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Get ready for an epic adventure at Babylon Park! London’s first-ever underground theme park is packed with exciting rides, awesome arcade games, and the city’s only indoor rollercoaster. It’s fun for all ages! Get your tickets today to enjoy unlimited access to 2 floors of epic rides and arcade games! Highlights 🤩 Enjoy unlimited access to 2 floors of epic rides including Tagada, Drop Tower, Bumper Cars, and more. 🎢 Zoom through the galaxy on the city’s only indoor rollercoaster. 🎮 Test your skills on tonnes of arcade games as many times as you can. 👶 Explore the 2 soft play zones —perfect for little explorers (individual tickets sold). 👽 Step into an alien-themed wonderland and be transported to outer space. 🥳 Ideal for birthday parties, team-building days, and other special occasions. Click here for more information on group bookings 🎁 Gift memories to someone special! Purchase a gift card for Babylon Park: London’s Underground Theme Park here General Info 🎟️Please note entry to the park is free. You can purchase tickets for unlimited access to all attractions and games! 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector 🕒 Opening hours: - Monday–Friday: 10:00 a.m. – 9:00 p.m. - Saturday: 10:00 a.m. – 10:00 p.m. - Sunday: 10:00 a.m. – 9:00 p.m. ⏳ Duration: Varies based on ticket purchased. Access begins when you receive your wristband on entry. 📍 Location: Babylon Park, Camden, London 👤 Age requirement: Babylon Park is perfect for adults and children of all ages. There is no minimum age requirement for the indoor theme park. The drop tower and rollercoaster have a height restriction. ♿ Accessibility: The venue is wheelchair accessible, however, the rides are not. ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Welcome to Babylon Park , London’s best-kept secret. As the city’s first-ever underground theme park, Babylon Park promises an epic day out—whatever the weather! Whether you’re zooming through space on London’s only indoor rollercoaster, testing your skills on epic arcade games, or getting creative in the play-and-colour zone, Babylon Park promises a fun-filled adventure for all ages. The best part? Your admission ticket offers you unlimited access to all attractions, so you can enjoy your favourites as many times as you like during your chosen time! Don’t miss out—get your tickets today!$$, $$GBP 8.75 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/309703$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/44786700-f5bd-11ef-8c72-a6d2952182ea$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/309703$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Harry Potter Warner Bros. Studios with Coach Transport from London$$, $$Warner Bros. Studio Tour London$$, null, 51.69014060000001, -0.4180303000000001, $$Parks & outdoor play$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Warner%20Bros.%20Studio%20Tour%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/139631$$, null, null, 0, $$All ages are welcome$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Harry Potter Warner Bros. Studios with Coach Transport from London Step into the Wizarding World of Harry Potter and immerse yourself in the magic! Highlights 🧙‍♂️ Step onto Platform 9¾, hop on the Hogwarts Express, and dive into Harry Potter's enchanting universe! 🏰 Discover iconic sets such as the Great Hall, Diagon Alley, and Snape's Dungeon 🎥 Explore the enchanting world of special effects and witness captivating real-life magic General Info 📅 Date and times: various dates available (select during purchase) ⏳ Duration: Total duration of the experience is 7 hours approximately (round trip transportation included) 📍 Location: Warner Bros. Studio Tour London (departure from London is at the Evan Evans office: 258 Vauxhall Bridge Rd) ❗ For this event, all sales are final and tickets can’t be refunded, changed or modified. For more information, please refer to our T&Cs 👤 Age requirement: All ages are welcome. Children under 16 must be accompanied by an adult Adult – Age: 16–99 Youth – Age: 5–15 Child – Age: 3–4 Infants (under 3 years old) join for free with a paying adult, but have to be seated on their parent's lap Description Step into the enchanting world of Harry Potter at our immersive event! Experience the wonder of the wizarding universe as you step onto Platform 9¾, board the Hogwarts Express, and embark on a thrilling journey. Explore iconic sets like the Great Hall, Diagon Alley, and Snape's Dungeon, and be captivated by the secrets of mind-blowing special effects that bring the magic to life. Don't miss this once-in-a-lifetime wizarding adventure! Get your tickets now for Harry Potter Warner Bros. Studios with Coach Transport from London!$$, $$GBP 55.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/139631$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/8291d96e-5149-11ee-8e81-a2654b591637$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/139631$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Peppa Pig Afternoon Tea London Sightseeing Bus Tour$$, $$Temple Embankment Bus Stop N, London$$, null, 51.51104065954276, -0.11286350314396541, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Temple%20Embankment%20Bus%20Stop%20N%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599704$$, null, null, 0, $$2+ ❗ Any allergies must be emailed and confirmed by management at bus@b-bakery$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Hop aboard the Peppa Pig Afternoon Tea London Sightseeing Bus Tour from Brigit’s Bakery for a fun-filled ride through London’s most iconic sights. With sweet treats, entertainment, and plenty of family fun, it’s an experience little ones won’t forget. Highlights 🐷 Enjoy a Peppa Pig-themed afternoon tea menu for all ages 🚌 Discover iconic London landmarks from a vintage double-decker 🎶 Sing along and play games with a lively onboard entertainer 🎁 Take home themed souvenirs and an activity book for added fun Dietary Requirements 🚩After booking, you’ll be asked to select your menu and share any dietary requirements. Please double-check your choices, as they cannot be changed once submitted.🚩 🎉 Looking for even more Peppa Pig fun in London? Don’t miss these special seasonal bus tours packed with themed treats, entertainment, and unforgettable moments for the whole family: 🎃 Peppa Pig Halloween Sightseeing Bus Tour – Hop aboard for a spook-tacular ride through London with festive fun, playful surprises, and Halloween-themed delights. Book your tickets here. 🎄 Peppa Pig Christmas Sightseeing Bus Tour – Experience London’s magical Christmas lights with seasonal treats, joyful entertainment, and plenty of holiday cheer. Book your tickets here. 🎁 Gift memories to someone special! Purchase a gift card for Peppa Pig Afternoon Tea London Sightseeing Bus Tour here General Info 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector ⏳ Duration: 1 hour and 30 minutes 📍 Departure: TEMPLE EMBANKMENT (BUS STOP N) 👤 Age requirement: 2+ ❗ Any allergies must be emailed and confirmed by management at bus@b-bakery.com ❗ ♿ Accessibility: please refer to the FAQs ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Climb aboard a charming double-decker for a Peppa Pig–themed afternoon tea through London’s iconic streets. Delight in a playful menu crafted for little ones and grown-ups alike, while onboard entertainment, sing-alongs, and interactive tablets bring the journey to life. With famous landmarks passing by and themed keepsakes to take home, it’s a magical family outing full of flavour and fun. Get your tickets for Peppa Pig Afternoon Tea London Sightseeing Bus Tour in London! © 2026 ABD Ltd/ Hasbro/HCPL Ltd.$$, $$GBP 39.22 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599704$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/02ede6a2-4891-11f1-858d-f6135ba131ed.png$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599704$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Mini Genius Lab: Cool Science Experiments for Kids$$, $$Gamepath Monopoly Basement, London$$, null, 51.5234882, -0.1367437, $$Museums & culture$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Gamepath%20Monopoly%20Basement%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/674657$$, null, null, 0, $$Designed for kids aged 6 and up$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Mini Genius Lab has arrived in London ! This hands-on lab adventure lets kids and parents dive into exciting science experiments with soap bubbles and smoky dry ice, all led by a hilarious “mad scientist”! Expect plenty of giggles, gasps, and ‘wow’ moments as you explore, learn, and have fun together . Get your tickets! Highlights 🧫 Make your own slime to take home and pop fun soap bubbles of all shapes ❄️ Watch dry ice swirl, fog, and fizz in jaw-dropping experiments 🧑‍🔬 Led by a high-energy “mad scientist” who makes learning unforgettable 👨‍👩‍👧 Quality time for parents and kids : make unforgettable memories together 🧽 100% hands-on fun for kids, 0% cleanup for parents! General Info 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector ⏳ Duration: 60 minutes 📍 Location: Gamepath Monopoly Basement, London 👤 Age recommendation: Designed for kids aged 6 and up. Younger children are welcome — they'll just need a little extra guidance from a parent or guardian. Babies (0–2) get in free. ♿ Accessibility: This venue is accessible ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Calling all curious minds and mini Einsteins! Mini Genius Lab is the ultimate science playground where imagination meets experimentation. With exciting activities that mix learning and laughter, this immersive workshop turns you and your kids into scientists for the day. It’s a chance to share smiles, snap great photos, and spark a lifelong love of science without any mess at home. Let the experiments begin. Get your tickets for Mini Genius Lab in London!$$, $$GBP 19.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/674657$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/3cc70810-1342-11f1-aea0-ee24abf6c566.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/674657$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Modern Magic Show with Jake Banfield$$, $$The Charlotte Street Hotel, London$$, null, 51.5183811, -0.135037000000011, $$Family activities$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=The%20Charlotte%20Street%20Hotel%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/117306$$, null, null, 0, $$All ages are welcome$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$🎁 Gift this experience to your loved ones! Click here to check out our gift card. Tickets for Modern Magic Show with Jake Banfield in London 🎫 Best Available Seat Ticket for 1 Highlights ✨ A mind-blowing magic show by the master of deceit, Jake Banfield 📺 R ecently seen reaching the live semi-finals of Britain’s Got Talent 🏙️ Cool and exclusive London location at The Charlotte Street Hotel 🍷 Purchase drinks to enjoy before and during the show from the guest only private bar General Info 📅 Date: select your dates directly in the ticket selector 🕒 Time: 8 p.m. (please arrive at 7:30 p.m.) ⏳ Duration: 1 hour and 10 minutes 📍 Location: The Charlotte Street Hotel, London 👤 Age requirement: All ages are welcome. Suitable for children 8 and above. 👗 Dress code: smart and chic Description Prepare yourself for a journey of dapper deception and mischievous mind games with Jake Banfield, fresh from reaching the live semi-finals of Britain’s Got Talent this year. Step inside one of London’s most stylish hidden spaces for an unforgettable evening of modern magic, mind-reading and impossible moments with Jake Banfield. From the sumptuous screening room at The Charlotte Street Hotel, get ready to have your mind read and your senses manipulated as you experience some of the most astonishing feats of modern magic. Blending cheeky showmanship, expert sleight of hand and the charm that made him a standout on BGT, Jake delivers an intimate, unforgettable evening of contemporary magic that will leave you speechless. Get your tickets now for the Modern Magic Show with Jake Banfield in London!$$, $$GBP 40.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/117306$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/339465c2-1197-11ed-8179-b2aa14fa840a.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/117306$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Space Explorers: The ISS Experience - London$$, $$Eclipso Cultural Adventures, London$$, null, 51.53952440537468, -0.14337720537981558, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Eclipso%20Cultural%20Adventures%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/651591$$, null, null, 0, $$8+$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Space Explorers: The ISS Experience is a large-scale free-roaming VR experience based on NASA missions. Travel 250 miles above Earth into the International Space Station (ISS) and discover what daily life in space is truly like. Walk alongside astronauts, admire breathtaking views of our planet and experience the vast immensity of the universe through spectacular footage filmed in space. Highlights 🌌 Step inside the International Space Station through an immersive free-roaming VR experience 📽️ Witness the first-ever spacewalk captured in cinematic virtual reality 🛰️ Explore an entirely walkable 3D model of the International Space Station 👩‍🚀 Walk alongside astronauts and discover life aboard the ISS 🌍 Experience breathtaking views of Earth captured during real NASA missions ☄️ A must-do immersive journey acclaimed by audiences worldwide 🎁 Gift memories to someone special! Purchase a gift card for Space Explorers: The ISS Experience - London here General Info 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector ⏳ Duration: the VR experience lasts approximately 40 minutes. Please arrive 10–15 minutes before the time indicated on your ticket for check-in and onboarding 📍 Location: Eclipso London – Camden 👤 Age requirement: 8+. Children must be accompanied by an adult ♿ Please note: this experience is not wheelchair accessible ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Welcoming over 500,000 visitors worldwide through Space Explorers: THE INFINITE, Space Explorers: The ISS Experience is now making its European debut in London with its new Free-Roaming Edition. Experience a large-scale free-roaming VR adventure showcasing life in space, featuring scenes and footage from the Emmy Award-winning series Space Explorers: The ISS Experience . Meet legendary astronauts, learn about their adventures and explore space without ever leaving the ground. It’s the closest most of us will ever get to the stars. Get your tickets for Space Explorers: The ISS Experience in London!$$, $$GBP 34.50 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/651591$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/99ce5672-5aa4-11f1-83cc-4edda567d35f.png$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/651591$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$The Jury Experience - The 20 Million Dollar Heist$$, $$Shaw Theatre, London$$, null, 51.528861, -0.128087, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shaw%20Theatre%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/338406$$, null, null, 0, $$Families and children$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$* { box-sizing: border-box; } img { max-width: 100%; } .tje-wrap { max-width: 100%; overflow-x: hidden; } .tje-section-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: #0f0f0f; margin: 0 0 0.875rem 0; position: relative; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; } .tje-section-title::after { content: ""; display: block; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 3rem; height: 4px; background: #C8222A; border-radius: 3px; } .tje-label-small { font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a8a8a; margin: 0 0 0.625rem 0; display: block; } .tje-intro { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #444; margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0; } .tje-hero-quote { position: relative; padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 1.75rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #C8222A; } .tje-hero-quote p { margin: 0; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 500; font-style: italic; color: #0f0f0f; letter-spacing: -0.01em; } .tje-hero-quote .quote-accent { color: #C8222A; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; } /* Show the line break only on mobile */ .tje-mobile-break { display: none; } @media (max-width: 48rem) { .tje-mobile-break { display: inline; } } .tje-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ece9e3; margin: 1.75rem 0; height: 0; } .tje-badges { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; } .tje-badge { font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; color: #090e12; padding: 0.35rem 0 0.1rem 0; border-top: 2px solid #B01C23; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-fl