($$Paradox Museum London - The Ultimate Birthday Party Venue in London$$, $$Paradox Museum London$$, null, 51.49970640000001, -0.1639623, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Paradox%20Museum%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/367302$$, null, null, 0, $$all ages welcome! Children under 14 years old must be accompanied by a paying adult$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$🎉 Exit reality. Enter birthday fun! Celebrate in style at Paradox Museum London! Host an unforgettable party surrounded by mind-bending illusions and interactive exhibits, followed by exclusive access to our private party room - The Dragon's Nest. A unique birthday experience in the heart of London, perfect for all ages! ✉ Important: At the screen after booking your birthday party, you will be asked to provide your email address so our team can contact you regarding any special requirements, including dietary needs, allergies or other preferences. Tickets for Birthday celebrations at Paradox Museum 🎫 The Mayfair Chippy Package: Includes full access to the museum (including our iconic Zero-Gravity Room) followed by 45 minutes in the Dragon's Nest birthday room for celebrations, plus hot food catering by Mayfair Chippy, cake, soft drinks and tableware (plates, cups, cutlery and napkins). Must be booked at least 5 days in advance. 🎫 VIP Birthday Package: Includes full access to the museum (including our iconic Zero-Gravity Room) followed by 45 minutes in the Dragon's Nest birthday room for celebrations, plus party catering (sandwiches, cake and soft drinks) and tableware (plates, cups and napkins). Must be booked at least 5 days in advance. 🎫 Standard Birthday Package: Includes full access to the museum (including our iconic Zero-Gravity Room) followed by 45 minutes in the Dragon's Nest birthday room for celebrations. Must be booked at least 2 days in advance. 🎫 Accompanying Adult: Includes full access to the museum (including our iconic Zero-Gravity Room) followed by 45 minutes in the Dragon's Nest birthday room for celebrations. This ticket doesn't include food . If attending adults would like food included, the tickets can be booked as 'Accompanying Adult' and upgraded to a food package (either the Mayfair Chippy or VIP option) for an additional charge. Please contact the venue to arrange the upgrade. Please note that each birthday package requires a minimum purchase of 2 adult tickets for the adults accompanying the children. 🔥​​​ Why Choose Paradox for your Birthday Event? 🌀 Explore over 50 immersive and mind-bending exhibits 🤳 Visit the Zero-Gravity Room - a surreal space adventure! 💫 Enjoy exclusive party room hire in London with themed décor. 🎁 Party bags with fun gifts for guests. 📸 Take the coolest selfies in impossible rooms - upside down, disappearing and more! 🎉 Bring your own decorations and food (except alcohol) 🍰 The VIP & Mayfair Chippy Birthday Packages include food, drinks and tableware - just show up and celebrate! 🎶 You are welcome to play your own music in the party room via your phone 🧠 Ideal for all ages - from kids birthday parties to teen and adult events. 👤 Up to 55 guests - contact us at london@paradoxmuseum.com for larger group bookings and custom requests ❓FAQs for Birthday celebrations at Paradox Museum here Birthday Party Details 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector ⏳ Duration: approx. 75 minutes in the museum followed by 45 minutes in the Dragon's Nest party room 📍 Location: Paradox Museum London, 90 Brompton Rd, SW3 1JJ 👤Age requirement: all ages welcome! Children under 14 years old must be accompanied by a paying adult. Photo ID will be required for minors aged 14-17 attending the museum without an adult. Children under 4 years old can enter the museum for free. 🌀 Zero-Gravity access: Children under the age of 18 must have an adult over the age of 18 consent to the T&Cs of the Zero Gravity exhibit on their behalf and accompany them at the Zero Gravity exhibit ♿ Accessibility: the venue is wheelchair accessible 👥Please note that all guests, both children and adults, attending the party are required to purchase the relevant Birthday Package Ticket. Prices are the same for adults and children ⚠ Tickets are not refundable ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Looking for unforgettable birthday party ideas for kids or teens in London? Paradox Museum London delivers the wow factor. With illusion-filled walkthroughs and hand-on interactive zones, it's more than just a venue - it's a fully immersive birthday experience your guests will rave about. Customise your celebration in the Dragon's Nest by playing your own party playlist or bringing themed decorations to make the space your own. Our team is here to make the entire experience smooth and memorable. Book your tickets now and celebrate your birthday at Paradox Museum London!$$, $$GBP 32.50 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/367302$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/9888f7ca-3b17-11f0-a380-fe43d2547f6a.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/367302$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Beauty & Wellness - Gift Card$$, $$Secret London Location$$, null, 51.50358749999999, -0.1112389, $$Family activities$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Secret%20London%20Location$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/306696$$, null, null, 0, $$Families and children$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$Gift Card for Beauty & Wellness 🥐 Official Gift Card for Beauty & Wellness plans in London. Treat yourself to a self-care experience, you'll get to choose from all the Beauty & Wellness plans on the Fever website and app. What's Included 🥐 A gift card valid for any Beauty & Wellness plan in London 🎫 The gift card voucher can be for 1 year Gift Card Info 📱 See information and instructions on how to use the gift card here 👉 Check out the best Beauty & Wellness plans in London Why Is this Fever Gift Card for You? Fever invites you to the best Beauty & Wellness experiences in town! Whether you want to treat yourself to a beauty treatment or you want to test your limits at a fitness or workout class, there are plenty of options in London. Discover your favorite events, choose your plan, and indulge in a fulfilling experience. The gift card is easy to use and valid for any Beauty & Wellness event... that's why it's the perfect treat for friends and family! Get your Beauty & Wellness Gift Card, valid for any Beauty & Wellness event in your city. Don't miss out! Fever_days_2026$$, $$GBP 30.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/306696$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/3db4a678-64ab-11f1-a52a-12b454e5dace.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/306696$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Tootbus London Discovery Bus Tour$$, $$The Original Tour, London$$, null, 51.5075713804373, -0.130582999652916, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=The%20Original%20Tour%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/112218$$, null, null, 0, $$all ages are welcome$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$📱 Smartphone tickets ⚡ Instant access to your tickets 🌐 Languages: audio guide included in English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Arabic, Chinese, Japanese, Russian, Portuguese Check out all the wonderful things London has to offer by hopping on the Tootbus London Discovery tour! Make your way around the heart of the city and see London's best landmarks. You could choose to see the Crown Jewels at the Tower of London, the Changing of the Guard at Buckingham Palace, or you could climb the dome of St Paul's Cathedral– the Discovery Bus Tour makes it easy to reach all these landmarks, hop off at the nearest bus stop and explore! Get your tickets for Tootbus London Discovery Bus Tour in London! Highlights 🚌 Explore London at your own pace with a hop-on hop-off bus tour 👂 Discover all the key facts about London through an included audio guide 🎡 See the city's top landmarks ✨ Enjoy unlimited journeys throughout the day What's included? ✔️ Earphones (bringing your own is encouraged) ✔️ Kids audio guide (available in English and French) ✔️ Tootbus app (with real-time bus tracking, audio commentary, and self-guided walking tours) ✔️Audio commentary on the bus in 10 languages ✔️ Free thematic walks: Royal family, and Kensington Gardens ✔️ Wi-fi onboard Locations and timings 📌 Yellow Route Monday to Thursday: buses run every 30 minutes Friday to Sunday: buses run every 40 minutes The bus can be boarded at any stop along the route and the main departure point is on the corner of Coventry Street and Whitcomb Street 📌 Blue Route All days: buses run every 40 minutes The bus can be boarded at any stop along the route and the main departure point is Grosvenor Gardens Additional Information 🕒 Times: - Weekdays: 9 a.m. - 4:20 p.m. - Weekends: 9 a.m. - 5 p.m. 👤 Age requirement: all ages are welcome. Children aged 16 and under must be accompanied by an adult (Age range: Adult 16+, Child 5–15, Infant 0–4) 🎫 Child: 5–15 🎫 Adult:16+ ♿ Accessibility: wheelchair/stroller accessible Why choose Fever? ✔️ Millions of users book every month. ✔️ The best prices and availability at all times. ✔️ Thousands of unique experiences. ✔️ Verified user reviews. ✔️ 24/7 customer service. All ticket sales are final and cannot be refunded, exchanged, or otherwise modified. Click here to check out the T&Cs .$$, $$GBP 13.63 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/112218$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/cb3b9294-aa9d-11ec-8342-76caf20dc8e2$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/112218$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$The Museum of Brands: A Visual Journey Through Consumer Culture$$, $$Museum of Brands, London$$, null, 51.5163994, -0.2110242, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Museum%20of%20Brands%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/110854$$, null, null, 0, $$Families and children$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$Tickets 🎫 Child Ticket (7-16) 🎫 Adult Ticket (17-59) 🎫 Concessions Ticket (60+) 🎫 Family Ticket (2 adults + 2 children) Children under the age of 7 are admitted for free Highlights 💸 Take a journey through history and consumer culture 📰 Over 12,000 items and design artefacts on display ✨ Temporary and permanent exhibitions 🏤 A small and quirky museum 💡 Perfect day out idea for families General Info 📅 Date: Mondays - Sundays (select during purchase) 🕒 Time: - Monday to Saturday from 10 a.m. - 6 p.m. - Sundays and Bank Holidays from 11 a.m. - 5 p.m. 📍 Location: The Museum of Brands ❓ For this event, all sales are final and tickets can’t be refunded, changed or modified. For more information, please refer to our T&Cs Description Take a nostalgic journey through 200 years of consumer culture, social change and lifestyle at the Museum of Brands, located in the heart of Notting Hill. Established in 1984, the museum features over 12,000 original items and images from iconic brands, as well as housing over half a million items. The collection aims to concentrate on areas that have transformed daily life– from entertainment, to children's toys, to wartime ephemera, royal souvenirs and more! Reflecting a vast social history and the evolution of consumer lifestyle, this museum is a must for fans of history, British culture, design, and commercial art.$$, $$GBP 14.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/110854$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/721c8556-949f-11ec-9cf7-7202d1a5cd48$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/110854$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Stranger Things: The First Shadow$$, $$Phoenix Theatre, London$$, null, 51.5144765, -0.1295084, $$Parks & outdoor play$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Phoenix%20Theatre%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/130434$$, null, null, 0, $$all ages welcome ♿ Accessibility: the venue is not wheelchair accessible Description Hawkins, 1959: a regular town with regular worries$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Written by Kate Trefry and original story by the Duffer Brothers, Stranger Things: The First Shadow is a gripping West End play that takes you back to the beginning, revealing Hawkins' story before the world turned upside down. Experience theatrical storytelling and stagecraft to a whole new dimension in this Stranger Things prequel at Phoenix Theatre, located in the heart of the West End between Soho and Covent Garden. Get your tickets! Tickets for Stranger Things: The First Shadow at Phoenix Theatre, London 🎫 Stalls 🎫 Dress Circle 🎫 Grand Circle Highlights 🤩 Enjoy a gripping new play taking you right back to the beginning of the Stranger Things story 🏘️ Find out what happened in Hawkins to iconic characters like Joyce, Hopper, and the origins of Henry Creel before the world turned upside down ✒️ Written by Kate Trefry and original story by the Duffer Brothers, the creators of the hit Netflix series Stranger Things ⭐ Brought to life by a multi-award-winning creative team, who take theatrical storytelling and stagecraft to a whole new dimension 🎭 Located in Phoenix Theatre, an iconic theatre in London’s West End General Info 📅 Date: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector 📍 Location: Phoenix Theatre (West End - Borough of Camden, London) 👤 Age requirement: all ages welcome ♿ Accessibility: the venue is not wheelchair accessible Description Hawkins, 1959: a regular town with regular worries. Young Jim Hopper’s car won’t start, Bob Newby’s sister won’t take his radio show seriously and Joyce Maldonado just wants to graduate and get the hell out of town. When new student Henry Creel arrives, his family finds that a fresh start isn’t so easy… and the shadows of the past have a very long reach. This gripping Stranger Things play takes you right back to the beginning of the story—and may hold the key to the end. Get your tickets for Stranger Things: The First Shadow at Phoenix Theatre in London’s West End! Created by Kate Trefry with original story by the Duffer Brothers, Jack Thorne & Kate Trefry. Based on the Netflix Series, 'Stranger Things', created by the Duffer Brothers. Directed by Stephen Daldry$$, $$GBP 42.00 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/130434$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/536cb870-f5b4-11ed-8d98-2e10c9f0cbeb.jpg$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/130434$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$),
($$Peppa Pig Halloween London Sightseeing Bus Tour$$, $$Temple Embankment Bus Stop N, London$$, null, 51.51104065954276, -0.11286350314396541, $$Music & singing$$, $$10:00$$, $$17:00$$, $$https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Temple%20Embankment%20Bus%20Stop%20N%2C%20London$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599654$$, null, null, 0, $$2+ ❗ Any allergies must be emailed and confirmed by management at bus@b-bakery$$, $$London$$, '{}', null, $$Select a live date and time on Fever before booking.$$, $$⭐ Don’t miss the Peppa Pig Halloween London Sightseeing Bus Tour from Brigit’s Bakery, a spooky afternoon tea experience through London’s most famous landmarks. Enjoy Halloween treats, family sing-alongs, and a best-dressed costume prize on this limited-time adventure. Highlights 🎃 Enjoy a spooky Peppa Pig Halloween afternoon tea with themed treats for kids and grown-ups 🚌 Discover iconic London sights including Big Ben and St Paul's Cathedral 🎶 Sing along to Peppa Pig songs with an interactive tablet animation at every table 🏆 Dress up in Halloween costumes for a chance to win the best-dressed family prize Dietary Requirements 🚩After booking, you’ll be asked to select your menu and share any dietary requirements. Please double-check your choices, as they cannot be changed once submitted.🚩 🎉 Looking for even more Peppa Pig fun in London? Don’t miss these special bus tours packed with themed treats, entertainment, and unforgettable moments for the whole family: 🐷 Peppa Pig Afternoon Tea London Sightseeing Bus Tour – Hop aboard for a delightful ride through London while enjoying a delicious themed afternoon tea, interactive entertainment, and plenty of Peppa Pig fun along the way. Book your tickets here. 🎄 Peppa Pig Christmas Sightseeing Bus Tour – Experience London’s magical Christmas lights with seasonal treats, joyful entertainment, and plenty of holiday cheer. Book your tickets here. General Info 📅 Dates and times: select your date & time directly in the ticket selector ⏳ Duration: 1 hour and 30 minutes 📍 Departure: TEMPLE EMBANKMENT (BUS STOP N) 👤 Age requirement: 2+ ❗ Any allergies must be emailed and confirmed by management at bus@b-bakery.com ❗ ♿ Accessibility: please refer to the FAQs ❓ Please consult the FAQs of this experience here Description Celebrate Halloween with Peppa Pig on a magical London sightseeing bus tour filled with spooky afternoon tea treats. Enjoy family sing-alongs, a Peppa Pig-guided animation on in-table tablets, and spectacular views of famous landmarks such as Big Ben and Tower Bridge. Costumes are encouraged, with a prize for the best-dressed family, making this limited-time adventure a fun-filled day for kids and grown-ups alike. Get your tickets for Peppa Pig Halloween London Sightseeing Bus Tour in London! © 2026 ABD Ltd/ Hasbro/HCPL Ltd.$$, $$GBP 39.22 from Fever$$, true, $$Fever London family listings$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599654$$, $$https://applications-media.feverup.com/image/upload/f_auto,w_720,h_720/fever2/plan/photo/d200cffe-4891-11f1-bbab-7e064463a3c7.png$$, $$https://feverup.com/m/599654$$, null, '{}'::date[], $$2026-07-11$$, null, '{}', $$date_range$$, $$Fever lists live availability in its ticket selector. Check Fever before booking.$$, $$published$$)
